/Z %	90
/bracketleft %	91
/backslash %	92	% /quotedblleft in TeX text
/bracketright %	93
/circumflex %	94	% /asciicircum in ASCII
/underscore %	95	% /dotaccent in TeX text
/quoteleft %	96	% /grave accent in ANSI
/a %	97
